channel.title: Changes to non-embedded code lists (21st July)
channel.description:
A heads up that the there is 1 planned change to non-embedded code lists which is planned to be taken forwards if no objection is received within 7 days. In summary this is:
- Add An Entry For IADB (Inter-American Development Bank) to the IATI Organisation Identifier Codelist
Further information on this change is available on the IATI support pages: http://support.iatistandard.org/entries/83276965-Add-An-Entry-For-IADB-to-the-IATI-Organisation-Identifier-Codelist
With best wishes, Dale
